    'https://www.euro-access.eu/en/calls',
    'KAVA Call 13: Call for Innovation & Education Projects',
    'KAVA Call 13: Call for Innovation & Education Projects',
    'short descriptionEIT RawMaterials is dedicated to advancing innovation within the raw materials value chain, nurturing groundbreaking ideas and projects that have the potential to make a significant impact. As part of our commitment to sustainable growth, we are also actively developing our financial sustainability strategy, as mandated by the EIT. The Innovation KAVA Projects are to contribute to these goals.',
    'short descriptionEIT RawMaterials is dedicated to advancing innovation within the raw materials value chain, nurturing groundbreaking ideas and projects that have the potential to make a significant impact. As part of our commitment to sustainable growth, we are also actively developing our financial sustainability strategy, as mandated by the EIT. The Innovation KAVA Projects are to contribute to these goals.',
    NULL,
    NULL,
    'https://www.euro-access.eu/en/calls/1762/KAVA-Call-13-Call-for-Innovation-amp-Education-Projects',
