    'short descriptionThe cooperation program Interreg VI A Mecklenburg-Vorpommern / Brandenburg / Poland 2021-2027 has published a new call for proposals for P2: Managing the consequences of climate change and preserving nature together and P3: Enabling better cross-border participation through language, culture and tourism.',
    'short descriptionThe cooperation program Interreg VI A Mecklenburg-Vorpommern / Brandenburg / Poland 2021-2027 has published a new call for proposals for P2: Managing the consequences of climate change and preserving nature together and P3: Enabling better cross-border participation through language, culture and tourism.',
